  <h1>Student Record Management System</h1>

  <p>
    This project is a simple <strong>Student Record Management System</strong> that allows users to manage student data effectively. The system is capable of:
  </p>

  <ul>
    <li>Adding new student records (Name, Roll Number, Marks)</li>
    <li>Sorting student records by name, roll number, or marks</li>
    <li>Viewing all student records in an organized format</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Add Student:</strong> Input student details such as name, roll number, and marks</li>
    <li><strong>Sort Students:</strong> Sort by Name, Roll Number, or Marks (ascending or descending)</li>
    <li><strong>View All:</strong> Display all students' records in a structured format</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Technologies Used</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Programming Language: C++</li>
    <li>Terminal -based interface</li>
    <li>Local Storage (Array)</li>
  </ul>

   

  

</body>
</html>
